# Ignore everything by default
*

# Whitelist our gitignore
!.gitignore

# Whitelist the FreeRTOS kernel source (what we'll modify)
!FreeRTOS/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/*.c
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/include/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/include/**
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/MemMang/**
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/ThirdParty/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/ThirdParty/GCC/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/ThirdParty/GCC/RP2040/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/ThirdParty/GCC/RP2040/**
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM0/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM0/**

# Whitelist the RP2040 demo directory (our working dir)
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Demo/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Demo/ThirdParty/
!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Demo/ThirdParty/Community-Supported-Demos/
