!FreeRTOS/FreeRTOS/Demo/ThirdParty/Community-Supported-Demos/CORTEX_M0+_RP2040/LedTest/**

# Always ignore build artifacts even in whitelisted dirs
**/build/
*.uf2
*.elf
*.o
*.d
!README.md
